      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/3125926-for-one-more-day">Quotes from Por un dia más</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;When someone is in your heart, they're never truly gone. They can come back to you, even at unlikely times.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/quotes/105030-when-someone-is-in-your-heart-they-re-never-truly-gone">2666 likes</a>
